About this item

  • PURCOLOR: See a wider spectrum of colors than traditional RGB models with PurColor. Purcolour makes watching films feel almost like you're there. It enables the TV to express a huge range of colours for optimized picture performance and an immersive viewing experience
  • CRYSTAL PROCESSOR W/ 4K UPSCALING: Watch the content you love upgraded to dazzling 4K resolution. Youll be able to better enjoy your TVs capabilities as the Crystal Processor automatically transforms color, sound and more
  • CONTRAST ENHANCER: Contrast Enhancer allows every image to appear natural and incredibly detailed. This innovative picture technology analyses regions of each image and dynamically adjust the contrast, resulting in an enhanced sense of depth and colour
  • MOTION XCELERATOR: Experience clear picture as Motion Xcelerator automatically estimates the motion information between frames and uses it to predict the subsequent frames in a manner that improves the smoothness of motion
  • HDR: High Dynamic Range increases the range of light levels on your TV so you can enjoy an enormous spectrum of colours and all the visual details in even the darkest scene
  • OBJECT TRACKING SOUND LITE: Get in the mix with Object Tracking Sound Lite. Youll hear 3D surround sound that follows the movement on screen using our incredible virtual top channel audio
  • EXPERIENCE THE ULTIMATE IN AUDIO IMMERSION BY ADDING A SAMSUNG SOUNDBAR: Surround yourself with sound from your Samsung TV and Soundbar orchestrated in an epic harmony with Samsung Q Symphony. Its a groundbreaking feature that seamlessly combines your soundbar and TV speakers, creating an expansive surround sound experience. Elevate your movie nights and gaming sessions with Q Symphony
  • SAMSUNG GAMING HUB: Gaming Hub acts as a convenient conduit to your favorite cloud gaming platforms, console games and standalone apps. It displays recommendations for other games across platforms, saving you time so you can speed-run the game selection process
  • AI ENERGY MODE: With AI Energy Mode, you can conserve power. Surrounding light levels are automatically detected and analyzed to adjust the brightness, reducing overall power consumption

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    PurColor Technology: Enhances color accuracy and vibrancy, making your viewing experience more immersive.
    Gaming Hub: Allows you to play the latest games from Xbox and other platforms directly on your TV without needing a console1.
    Smart TV Powered by Tizen: Access a wide range of apps, including Netflix, Disney+, and more, all in one place.
    Excellent Picture Quality: The 4K resolution and PurColor technology provide sharp, vibrant images that enhance your viewing experience1.
    User-Friendly Interface: The Tizen OS is intuitive and easy to navigate, making it simple to find and enjoy your favorite content.
    Versatile Gaming Options: The Gaming Hub is a standout feature for gamers, offering access to a variety of games without the need for additional hardware.
    Affordable: Compared to other models in its class, the DU7100 offers great value for its price.
    The Samsung 60-inch Crystal UHD DU7100 Series TV is a fantastic option for those looking for a budget-friendly 4K TV with a range of smart features. Its excellent picture quality, user-friendly interface, and gaming capabilities make it a versatile choice for any household. However, if top-tier HDR performance and sound quality are critical for you, you might want to consider higher-end models.
